---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Manifesto" description="The mission behind OpenAgent.bot." path="/manifesto">
  <section class="shell text-page">
    <span class="eyebrow">Manifesto</span>
    <h1 class="serif">The open AI web needs better shelves.</h1>
    <p>
      Open-source AI work is scattered across repositories, model hubs, docs, posts,
      Discords, and release notes. OpenAgent.bot exists to turn that noise into clear,
      durable resource pages that can serve both human readers and automated systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      The first promise is simple: stable pages, honest summaries, useful categories,
      and a structure that can expand without becoming heavy.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .text-page {
    max-width: 820px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
    padding-top: 58px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
  }
</style>
